activities.activityName: Go for a walk with a book that you won't read
outcomes: I got interviewed by a TikToker and the Internet made fun of me :(
I didn't remember to take out the book of my tote bag, but someone gifted me a massage coupon!!
A cute person sat next to me and asked for books recommendations... and my number!!!
I tried doing the Astavakrasana but my hand slipped and it hurt so much :,(
I believe I reached the Nirvana and now I don't have problems sleeeping!!!
I became intimate with the modern moms and they gifted me a pricey necklace!
The treadmill outruned me and I fell in a ridiculous way to the floor :(
The gym was empty and I could blast out loud Taylor Swift without any judgement from the gymbros
I lifted more weight than the noisy gymbro and make him cry!!!!!!!
There was nothing cute of my size and I started crying in the middle of the shopping center
I exited one shop without paying and nobody noticed... oops!
Everything I wanted was half-priced and I even got gifted a curious book!!
I was crying so bad watching Lorelai and Rory love each other so much that the pizza on the oven got burn
I wanted to be like Rory so I read an intellectual book in one sitting
I got moved so much by the relation of Emily and Lorelai that I called my mother to ask how is her life
I mistook my glass of wine and drank the dirty water instead... IT WAS HORRIBLE!
I ended with my hands lilac, stained the t-shirt of the person next to me without them knowing and ran away with it!!
The hot teacher was impressed by my painting and went down their knees to ask me on a date!!!
I got distracted learning a choreography, and burnt the cookies in the oven :(
I got the quantities wrong, so now I got cookies for a whole week!
My cute and silly neighbour smelt my cookies and I invited them to stay the night...
Never in my life have I been surrounded by so many monkey dudes that I had to ran away crying!!
I unplugged the mixing desk while nobody was watching and use the distraction to fill my pockets with the telephones of the annoying dudes... oops!
I got everyone to burn down the dance floor to the beat of Sophie!! I was born to do this!
I had to fought a spider's nest and couldn't end cleaning :( IT WAS HORRIBLE!
I got distracted while cleaning with things I didn't remember having and found money under the bed!
I feel life is worth living again, everything is in order and so is my life!

activities.activityName: Call mom and listen to her complains
outcomes: We ended up yelling at each other because of a misunderstanding!! HATE HER!!
I left the telephone in the room while I showered and when I went back she was still talking alone... sorry not sorry!
I realised I have grown old just as my mother, and although she is guilty of part of my pain, I understand her...

activities.activityName: Write fanfics with the lights off
outcomes: A screenshot of my fic went viral on Twitter and everybody made fun of me!!
The omegaverse fans praised my fic and made me an internet sensation... Yuhu! I guess?
'The Lovely Adventures of Paquita and Fernandito' became an internet sensation and they offered me a publishing contract!!

activities.activityName: Go vintage shopping with a cute hat
outcomes: Nobody complemented my avant garde hat and I bought a scabies dress without knowing! WORST EXPERIENCE EVER!
I found the perfect skirt to match my extravagant hat! Life is worth living!
An alternative hot looking person complemented my outfit and asked for my number!!!
The neighbours heard my laments and called the police to see if something was wrong... EMBARRASSING!!
I cried in silence all night long and wake up refreshed and thinking life is about the ups and the downs
I tweeted how much I liked a certain sad singer song, and they replied and asked me on a date! Feeling like Paul Mescal rn...
My friends were #TeamJacob (ew), so I fought with them! They are never entering my house till they rethink it!
I dreamt a hot vampire lured me into the dark and now I wait every night by the window...
We all bonded talking and dreaming about Edward Cullen (Edward, if you ever read this, call me up!!)
My legs hurt so much that I had to exit crawling!!!
I bonded with the lonely ladies in the corner and started dancing together till the floor fell down!!!
I fell off the horse straight into the strong arms of a cowboy and ride all night long... yeah!
They brought me out on stage to laugh at my appearance! I wasted so much money on this horrible show
At the entrance they thought I was the leading lady and I entered free... Everything is better when is free!
I mistook the bathroom for the backstage and I crash into the lead actor! They sang me a ballad and I've never felt more love!'
I waited for hours and NOBODY came! I will never trust again...
The french person I sold my puked t-shirt gave me three times the price I asked! Sometimes I do like France...
The lovely old lady that bought my lilac skirt, told me a beautiful story when she was younger... I went back home crying, life is beautiful...
I can't believe it! They disconnected my microphone and yelled at me!! People are horrible sometimes...
Went with my friends and have so much fun! They invited us to drinks all night long!
I started singing 'I Will Always Love You' and a hot looking person climbed to the stage to sing with me. We even shared microphone... and numbers!

activities.activityName: Try to go to an opera without tickets
outcomes: I almost got in, but when they revised the tickets the police arrived and put on a show! I feel very embarrassed
The opera was the worst thing I've seen in years, but luckily they'd the comfiest armchairs and I slept all the time!
They sat me next to the composer and they asked me to be their secret lover for the night... That's not all, because later they asked for my number and promised to call!

activities.activityName: Steal from The Bazaar Next Door
outcomes: THEY CAUGHT ME! The lady saw me through the cameras and banned me from ever entering... I guess I deserve it...
You haven't heard this from me, but everything is better if you didn't pay for it!
The manager caught me, but when they grabbed my hand I started dancing to distract them... They fell in love with my forbidden steps!

activities.activityName: Have a photo shoot with friends
outcomes: I tried doing a risky tumblr-esque pose, but my friend pulled my braid and almost snitched my wig!
My friend doesn't know how to take good photos of me, but all I want from them is to spend time together
Going out with my friends remained me of 2014, when wearing black lipstick and listening to Lorde was my life... My friends are the only ones that persevere over time!
My best friend revealed she has been dating a 60 year old man! MY GRANDFATHER BROTHER!
We thought someone in town went missing, and when we thought we had uncovered the true... We saw them go out of my old neighbour house... weird...
'Whatcha Say' started playing on the aux as all the gossip started intertwining: secret pregnancies, secret lovers and liars uncovered... We are Gossip Girl!

activities.activityName: Go to the library and act mysterious
outcomes: I was walking through the aisles when a child started throwing me books to my face!! He gave me a bruise!!!
On the second floor, hidden behind some sofas, I found a strange book that says that if you arrange eight flowers, you can open a portal... Trying it tonight!
A blond guy from across the table threw me a note inviting me to a secret society party... I couldn't say no!! Maybe he is rich and I can finally live my dream...

activities.activityName: Try to go to a movie premiere
outcomes: I tried sneaking in through the cleaning service door... AND THEY PUT ME TO WORK ALL NIGHT LONG!!
At first it was a bit weird being alone, but I enjoyed the movie a lot! I logged it into my Moviebox right when I arrived home! 4.5 stars and a heart
I GOT IN! But that's not all, because they sat me next to the lead actor and at the end of the movie he asked me to be his secret partner! Living the Hollywood Life

activities.activityName: Go to Mueblitex and redecorate the house
outcomes: I wanted to try a bed AND I FELL ASLEEP IMMEDIATELY! I was sleeping for THREE hours until the police had to wake me up! #Embarrassing
I had to leave behind a wonderful cushion and a bunch of candles, but my pocket was not ready for buying everything!
I had a magic coupon that save me half the price in everything I bought! My house is looking like those aesthetic Pictiritis boards
WHY NOBODY TOLD ME LA LA LAND WAS A CRYING MOVIE?! I stayed all night crying, this is so unfair!!!
13 going on 30, 10 Things I Hate About You, (500) Days of Summer, How To Lose a Guy in 10 Days... There's something with rom-coms with numbers in the title
I watched the Before Sunrise trilogy in one sitting... Best movie ever! Love is walking a city and forgetting planes and trains exist

activities.activityName: Write an article in the Carrie Bradshaw way
outcomes: I don't know when I thought it was a good idea to post it on social media... 100 unfollows in an hour!!! #NeverPuttingMyselfOutThereAgain
Well, I'm glad I can have hobbies, because writing may not be my thing... But it was fun trying!
Maybe it was the drink, but I felt shameless enough to send it to a magazine... AND THEY WANTED TO PUBLISH IT!! New York here I come!
